      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an unrivaled example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. With its flawless exterior finish and a cabin that retains its original factory freshness, this motorcar offers an 'as-new' driving experience for the sophisticated enthusiast. We invite you to inspect this pristine specimen, which stands as a testament to superior care and meticulous preservation.",
