    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, so the paint is sparkling and the interior is absolutely spotless. It drives like a dream and has been my total pride and joy. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s in tip-top shape and ready for a new home, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 45500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
